data.description: A charming three bedroom, two and a half bath home on a spacious lot with no HOA! Built in 2023, this home features a two car garage, an open downstairs floor plan with plenty of natural light, granite countertops and stainless-steel appliances in the kitchen, a gas fireplace, vaulted ceilings in the living room and master bedroom, a deck overlooking a huge, partially fenced-in backyard with 6ft wooden privacy fence and much more! Located just outside of Wilson, this property allows home buyers to enjoy all the perks of country living, while in close proximity to restaurants and shopping. Seller is a licensed real estate agent.
